failure.message:
The balance on the card should decrease by the price of one hearty meal. 
Check the code terminal = new PaymentTerminal(); card = new PaymentCard(10); terminal.eatHeartily(card); card.balance();
 expected:<5.7> but was:<10.0>

The balance on the card should drop to zero if we buy an affordable meal when the balance is exactly the price of that meal. Check the code:
terminal = new PaymentTerminal(); card = new PaymentCard(2.5); terminal.eatAffordably(card); card.balance();
 expected:<0.0> but was:<2.5>

The balance on the card should decrease by the price of one affordable meal. Check the code:
terminal = new PaymentTerminal(); card = new PaymentCard(10); terminal.eatAffordably(card); card.balance();
 expected:<7.5> but was:<10.0>
